{"tid":1061945,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"跟女友大波「沙律」有結婚打算？ 林耀聲：要保持神秘","createTime":"2019-03-14T18:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T22:26:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"66d19cee0e82b7d4440efae4137cf47202d90cc2","tid":1061945,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T18:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190314/s00009/de05ffea98f2220e9e85187bd171bf75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190314%2Fs00009%2Fde05ffea98f2220e9e85187bd171bf75.jpg&h=9d81cb40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由林耀聲、馬志威和楊柳青主演的電影《入鐵籠》，昨晚於又一城舉行首映禮。林耀聲女友張沛樂（沙律）到場撐男友，沙律透露媽媽都有來，還見到男友的爸爸，今次是雙方家長首次見面。<br />\n<br />\n問到他們拍拖三年，有沒有結婚計劃？林耀聲謂要保持神秘，大波沙律則表示想大家做好工作，才考慮結婚。至於二人相處之道？林耀聲指女友很尊重他，經常問他意見及由他話事。"},{"pid":"4bfd31e00bf5f8e87182927ed3f846415e30cfaa","tid":1061945,"uid":5180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T18:32:37.000Z","msg":"大波沙律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又幾好聽"},{"pid":"d670957437d17fa4ae183608ca81c32685b30016","tid":1061945,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T18:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LopW6Jw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLopW6Jw.png&h=97e77f4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b3e7891f79163406626f2a4d876a9c65dc608c0","tid":1061945,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d670957437d17fa4ae183608ca81c32685b30016","tid":1061945,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T18:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LopW6Jw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLopW6Jw.png&h=97e77f4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T22:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yTkCSqa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn